title: 720p Quinn

embed.description: wie feather hat ein video hochgeladen

body:
**Hiya!**

Ya boi is trying to reach a greater audience, because I will be doing a whole lot more of those. 
I'm a super tiny channel with merely two videos; this one being my 'better' version of the first 
and of course with more champions to come.

Therefore every single upvote on this post, subscribe on youtube and whatever possible action is really valuable to me, since it will
keep everyone who interested in this kind of thing updated and more people to find my channel. 

I hope you had as much fun watching the video, as I had editing.

Cheers,
Feather
{{sticker:sg-jinx}}
